snippet: A New York police officer traveling with Vice President Joseph R. Biden Jr. sustained minor injuries to his neck, back and chest when his motorcycle toppled over on the Grand Central Parkway.
lead_paragraph: A New York police officer traveling with Vice President Joseph R. Biden Jr. sustained minor injuries to his neck, back and chest when his motorcycle toppled over on the Grand Central Parkway.

headline.main: Officer in Biden Motorcade Is Hurt When Motorcycle Falls in Queens
